# 🎬 X-Tube: A MERN-Based YouTube Clone

## 🚀 Overview
X-Tube is a **YouTube-like video-sharing platform** built using the **MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js) stack**. This platform enables users to **upload, share, like, dislike, comment on videos, and download** content. It also features a **real-time chat system** powered by **Socket.io**.

---

## 🌟 Features

### 📹 Video Features
- ✅ Upload and manage videos
- ✅ Watch videos in different categories
- ✅ Like 👍 & Dislike 👎 videos
- ✅ Download 📥 videos for offline viewing
- ✅ Add videos to the **Watch Later** playlist
- ✅ Search 🔍 and filter videos by category
- ✅ Share 📤 videos with others

### 💬 Chat Features
- ✅ Real-time chat with **Socket.io**
- ✅ Private and group messaging
- ✅ Online/offline status tracking
- ✅ Emoji and media support 🎉

### 🔒 Authentication & Security
- ✅ **JWT Authentication** for secure login & sign-up
- ✅ Google OAuth authentication 🌍
- ✅ Secure video access and role-based permissions

### 📊 Additional Features
- ✅ Dark Mode 🌙 / Light Mode ☀️
- ✅ Responsive UI for **mobile & desktop** 📱💻
- ✅ Admin Dashboard for managing content

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### **Frontend** - [React.js](https://react.dev/)
- **React Router** for navigation
- **Redux Toolkit** for state management
- **Tailwind CSS** for a modern UI
- **Axios** for API requests

### **Backend** - [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) & [Express.js](https://expressjs.com/)
- **MongoDB** & **Mongoose** for database
- **Socket.io** for real-time chat
- **JWT (JSON Web Tokens)** for authentication
- **Cloudinary** for video storage

### **Deployment**
- **Frontend**: [Vercel](https://vercel.com/)  
  **Live URL:** [X-Tube Frontend](https://x-tube-chat-uait.vercel.app/)
- **Backend**: [Koyeb](https://www.koyeb.com/)  
  **Live URL:** [X-Tube API](https://ashamed-georgina-ziaurrehmanx-8e9ce942.koyeb.app/)

---

## 🎯 Installation & Setup

### 1️⃣ Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/x-tube.git
cd x-tube
```

### 2️⃣ Backend Setup
```bash
cd backend
npm install
npm start
```

### 3️⃣ Frontend Setup
```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm start
```

---

## 📜 API Endpoints
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/auth/signup` | Register a new user |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/login` | Login user |
| `GET` | `/api/videos/` | Fetch all videos |
| `POST` | `/api/videos/upload` | Upload a new video |
| `POST` | `/api/chat/send` | Send a chat message |
| `GET` | `/api/chat/messages` | Get all chat messages |

